Quickstrike:




Quickstrike turned his head and shoulder to Dark Mouse. "Ol' toad-bot back 
there told me that th' bunker is...below us?" He looked back down at the 
iron plate on the ground. "Wanna lift that up? Ah ain't got th' fingers fer 
it." he said to her, fearing that he would smash his fingers or the tip of 
his cobra arm. He was the bot that had the worst time when it came to 
handling things.
